  "wave_2_per_point": "sw=int(3*sample);\n\nfnZ=t4*t2-t5*t1;\n\np1=3*equal(sw,0)*sample;\np2=equal(sw,1)*3*(sample-.333);\np3=equal(sw,2)*3*(sample-.666);\n\nn1 = t2*fnZ-t8*t3;\nn2 = -(t1*fnZ-t7*t3);\nn3 = t1*t8-t2*t7;\n\nmx=p1*t7 +p2*n1 +p3*t1;\nmy=p1*t8 +p2*n2 +p3*t2;\nmz=p1*fnZ+p2*n3 +p3*t3;\n\nx=.14+.05*mx;\ny=.14+.05*my*1.25;\na=1-( above(sample,.33)*below(sample,.34) + above(sample,.66)*below(sample,.67));\n\nr=equal(sw,0);\ng=equal(sw,1);\nb=equal(sw,2);",
