  "wave_3_per_point": "t=(t1+(0+sample)*t2);\nt=if(above(t,1),t-1,t);\nt=t*6.2831;\n\nmx=cos(t)*sin(.43+2*t+3.1415*sin(2.98+2*t));\nmy=cos(1.9+.7*t)*sin(t);\nmz=cos(1.54+2*t)*sin(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t));\n\nfdX=2*cos(t)*(1+3.1415*cos(2.98+2*t))*cos(.43+2*t+3.1415*sin(2.98+2*t))-sin(t)*sin(.43+2*t+3.1415*sin(2.98+2*t));\nfdY=cos(1.9+.7*t)*cos(t)-.7*sin(1.9+.7*t)*sin(t);\nfdZ=cos(1.54+2*t)*cos(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t))*(2-6.2831*sin(1.01+2*t))-2*sin(1.54+2*t)*sin(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t));\ninvFDmag=1/sqrt( fdX*fdX + fdY*fdY + fdZ*fdZ );\n\nsdX=-4*cos(.43+2*t+3.1415*sin(2.98+2*t))*(sin(t)+3.1415*sin(2.98+3*t))-cos(t)*(5+25.132*cos(2.98+2*t)+39.4761*sqr(cos(2.98+2*t)))*sin( .43+2*t+3.1415*sin(2.98+2*t));\nsdY=-1.4*cos(t)*sin(1.9+.7*t)-1.49*cos(1.9+.7*t)*sin(t);\nsdZ=-12.566*cos(1.01+2*t)*cos(1.54+2*t)*cos(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t))+8*cos(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t))*(-1+3.1415*sin(1.01+2*t))*sin(1.54+2*t) - 4*cos(1.54+2*t)*(2-6.2831*sin(1.01+2*t)+9.869*sqr(sin(1.01+2*t)))*sin(2*t+3.1415*cos(1.01+2*t));\n\nsnX=fdY*sdZ-sdY*fdZ;\nsnY=fdZ*sdX-fdX*sdZ;\nsnZ=fdX*sdY-fdY*sdX;\ninvSNmag=1/sqrt( snX*snX+snY*snY+snZ*snZ );\nsnX=snX*invSNmag;\nsnY=snY*invSNmag;\nsnZ=snZ*invSNmag;\n\nfdX=fdX*invFDmag;\nfdY=fdY*invFDmag;\nfdZ=fdZ*invFDmag;\n\nfnX=snY*fdZ-fdY*snZ;\nfnY=snZ*fdX-snX*fdZ;\nfnZ=snX*fdY-snY*fdX;\n\nangl=6.2831*cos(628.3185*sample+2.54+40*sin(62.8318*sample+.56));\nrr=t3*(.1+2*abs(sin(628.3185*sample+2.54+40*cos(62.8318*sample+.56))));\nmx=mx+rr*cos(angl);\nmy=my+rr*(cos(angl)/sin(angl));\nmz=mz+rr*sin(angl);\n\nqq9=q4*q2-q5*q1;\nvx=(q7*mx+q8*my+qq9*mz-(t6*q7+t7*q8+t8*qq9));\nvy=(q4*mx+q5*my+q6*mz-(t6*q4+t7*q5+t8*q6));\nvw=q1*mx+q2*my+q3*mz-(t6*q1+t7*q2+t8*q3);\n\nox=(vx/vw)*.15;\noy=(vy/vw)*.15*1.25;\nx=.5-oy;\ny=.5+ox*1.25;\na=above(vw,.01)*pow(2*(.5-min(vw,.5)),2);"
